     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           @LST    1
      *----------------*
      *キーフィールド*
      *----------------*
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           C2SHN1
     C                     KFLD           C2SHN2
     C                     KFLD           C2SHN3
     C                     KFLD           KOTE
     C                     KFLD           @KOJ
     C                     KFLD           TKR1
     C                     KFLD           TKR2
     C                     KFLD           TKR3
     C                     KFLD           TKR4
      *
     C           KEY2      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           @JNEN   40
     C                     KFLD           MMJHN1
     C                     KFLD           MMJHN2
     C                     KFLD           MMJHN3
      *
