      *画面年変換*
      *------------*
     C                     MOVEL'*'       $$KBN   1
     C                     MOVEL@HIZ      PHIZ    4
     C                     CALL 'DATR00'
     C                     PARM           PHIZ    4
     C                     PARM           PPHZ    6
